rse rider\", \"from\": 2254, \"to\": 2269}, {\"ngram\": \"the pale horse\", \"from\": 2296, \"to\": 2310}, {\"ngram\": \"rider\", \"from\": 2315, \"to\": 2320}, {\"ngram\": \"Revelation\", \"from\": 2324, \"to\": 2334}, {\"ngram\": \"Hell\", \"from\": 2356, \"to\": 2360}, {\"ngram\": \"Joan\", \"from\": 2389, \"to\": 2393}, {\"ngram\": \"Arc\", \"from\": 2397, \"to\": 2400}, {\"ngram\": \"their patron Saint\", \"from\": 2446, \"to\": 2464}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Awareness and being mindful of the absurdity of violence are not exactly character traits of conservative evangelicalism.\\\"\", \"from\": 2467, \"to\": 2590, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Awareness\", \"from\": 2468, \"to\": 2477}, {\"ngram\": \"the absurdity\", \"from\": 2499, \"to\": 2512}, {\"ngram\": \"violence\", \"from\": 2516, \"to\": 2524}, {\"ngram\": \"character traits\", \"from\": 2541, \"to\": 2557}, {\"ngram\": \"conservative evangelicalism\", \"from\": 2561, \"to\": 2588}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But awareness and being mindful of the absurdity of violence are not exactly character traits of conservative evangelicalism, given that thePublic Religion Research Institutefound Republicans are 2.5 times more likely than Democrats to support political violence.\", \"from\": 2592, \"to\": 2855, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2772, \"end\": 2783, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republicanism\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0796111559627142e-18, \"text\": \"Republicans\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republicanism\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republicanism\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"awareness\", \"from\": 2596, \"to\": 2605}, {\"ngram\": \"the absurdity\", \"from\": 2627, \"to\": 2640}, {\"ngram\": \"violence\", \"from\": 2644, \"to\": 2652}, {\"ngram\": \"character traits\", \"from\": 2669, \"to\": 2685}, {\"ngram\": \"conservative evangelicalism\", \"from\": 2689, \"to\": 2716}, {\"ngram\": \"Democrats\", \"from\": 2815, \"to